• Aromatic VPH/EPH >C5 - C44 concentration of 137 ug/l; 
• VPH/EPH >C5 - C44 concentration of 1040 ug/l;
• Aliphatic EPH >C16 - C35 concentration of 765 ug/l;
• Aromatic EPH >C10 - C44 concentration of 137 ug/l;
• BOD concentration of 52 mg/l O2;
• Chloride concentration of 105 mg/l;
• COD concentration of 327 mg/l O2;
• Suspended Solids concentration of 128 mg/l;
• O-Phosphate concentration of 0.17 mg/l P;
• Total Phosphorus concentration of 0.52 mg/l P;
• Total Nitrogen concentration of 3.7 mg/l N, and
• Zinc concentration of 500 µg/l.

This is a non-compliance with Condition 6.1 of the licence.

You are reminded that failure to comply with any condition attached to a licence or revised licence is an offence.
